introduction: Overview (1)Born	December 17, 1984 in Stockport, Cheshire, England, UKMini Bio (1)Kerry Bennett is a British actress, born in Stockport, England, to a Seychellois mother and English father. She attended East 15 Acting School in London for 4 years on the BA Acting course.
